## Context.ContextTokens.parseContextQualifierToken() method

Parses a [context qualifier token](./ts-res.contextqualifiertoken.md) and validates it against the qualifiers present in the supplied [qualifier collector](./ts-res.qualifiers.ireadonlyqualifiercollector.md)<!-- -->.

**Signature:**

```typescript
static parseContextQualifierToken(token: string, qualifiers: IReadOnlyQualifierCollector): Result<IValidatedContextQualifierValueDecl>;
```
